9. Termination

Rights under this license terminate automatically if Licensee breaches the
license and does not cure the breach within fifteen days after written notice.
For deliberate threshold avoidance, unpaid production Commercial Use above the
Revenue Threshold, or removal of license notices, termination is immediate.

After termination, Licensee must stop using and distributing the Covered
Software, delete hosted copies under its control, and pay any unpaid royalties,
audit costs, interest, and enforcement costs allowed by law.

